# The `CompileUnit` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

Stores all information related to a compile unit, be it in its original instance of the object file or its brand new cloned and generated <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> tree. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

Stores all information related to a compile unit, be it in its original instance of the object file or its brand new cloned and generated <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> tree.

NOTE: we need alignment of at least 8 bytes as we use <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/pointerintpair">PointerIntPair&lt;CompileUnit &#42;, 3&gt;</a> in the <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/dwarflinker/lib/dwarflinker/parallel/dependencytracker-h">DependencyTracker.h</a>

Definition at line 53 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/dwarflinker/lib/dwarflinker/parallel/dwarflinkercompileunit-h">DWARFLinkerCompileUnit.h</a>.

<SectionDefinition>
